      "date": "2012-06-01 07:02:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nIt seems to most of this patch is just renaming and restructure. I did not see any logic changes. So I did not review very carefully. But it looks good to me.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
